<subSubSection id="C34015E2FF84FF98FDB4D518BDC9FA6A" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BE54669FF84FF98FDB4D518BDC9FA6A" blockId="26.[533,1535,484,1480]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">
<emphasis id="B92E9A7BFF84FF98FDB4D518BC4DFA20" bold="true" box="[565,774,1386,1410]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">
Recorded at: 
<collectingRegion id="499E888BFF84FF98FD46D518BC4DFA20" box="[711,774,1386,1410]" country="Malaysia" name="Perlis" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">Perlis</collectingRegion>
</emphasis>
: Bukit Jerneh Cave and Tumang Lembing Cave [
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB3B98FF84FF98FA91D518BA62FA20" author="Douangboubpha B &amp; Bumrungsri S &amp; Soisook P &amp; Murray SW &amp; Puechmaille SJ &amp; Satasook C" box="[1296,1321,1386,1410]" journalOrPublisher="Acta Chiropt." pageId="26" pageNumber="27" pagination="29 - 50" part="12" refId="ref39009" refString="30. Douangboubpha B, Bumrungsri S, Soisook P, Murray SW, Puechmaille SJ, Satasook C, et al. A taxonomic review of Hipposideros halophyllus, with additional information on H. ater and H. cineraceus (Chiroptera: Hipposideridae) from Thailand and Myanmar. Acta Chiropt. 2010; 12 (1): 29 - 50." title="A taxonomic review of Hipposideros halophyllus, with additional information on H. ater and H. cineraceus (Chiroptera: Hipposideridae) from Thailand and Myanmar" type="journal article" year="2010">30</bibRefCitation>
], Bukit Lagi [
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB3B98FF84FF98FA3BD518BAABFA20" author="Zubaid A." box="[1466,1504,1386,1410]" journalOrPublisher="Mammalia." pageId="26" pageNumber="27" pagination="134 - 136" part="52" refId="ref43825" refString="145. Zubaid A. Food habits of Hipposideros pomona (Chiroptera: Rhinolophidae) from Peninsular Malaysia. Mammalia. 1988; 52 (1): 134 - 136." title="Food habits of Hipposideros pomona (Chiroptera: Rhinolophidae) from Peninsular Malaysia" type="journal article" year="1988">145</bibRefCitation>
]. 
<taxonomicName id="4C5A3DEAFF84FF98FD94D5FCBDC1FA07" authorityName="Andersen" authorityYear="1918" box="[533,650,1421,1445]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pomona">
<emphasis id="B92E9A7BFF84FF98FD94D5FCBD62FA07" box="[533,553,1422,1445]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B92E9A7BFF84FF98FDB4D5FCBDC1FA07" box="[565,650,1422,1445]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">pomona</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a cave dweller and has been recorded from various forest 
<typeStatus id="54E1F8CBFF84FF98FA84D5FFBA77FA07" box="[1285,1340,1421,1445]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">types</typeStatus>
and disturbed areas [
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB3B98FF84FF98FDDBD5C2BD38FA6A" author="Francis CM" box="[602,627,1456,1480]" journalOrPublisher="New Holland Publishers" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" refId="ref38235" refString="14. Francis CM. A field guide to the mammals of South-East Asia. New Holland Publishers; 2008." title="A field guide to the mammals of South-East Asia" type="book" year="2008">14</bibRefCitation>
].
</paragraph>
